commit_message: Fixing lack of controls over MAXCHRS counters to avoid exceeding the limit
Fixing counting twice the last bin/position pos2 when updating counts of SAM reads
Merge branch 'main' of https://github.com/eblancoga/seqcode into main
Increasing the maximum number of chromosomes (ChromInfo.txt)
Increasing MAXLINE to 10000 for long RefSeq lines
Increasing MAXLINE ro 3000 for long RefSeq lines
Increasing MAXLINE ro 2000 for long RefSeq transcripts
